CSF is commonly used firewall that provides a good level of protection with easy to manage commands. It is used for Login/Intrusion detection, SSH login notification, Excessive connection blocking, Suspicious file reporting etc.

We will go through the Configuration of CSF in cPanel server and also the basic and most important configuration options in CSF configuration as below.

Configure VPS (Cents os) :-
===========================

Firewall installation in shell:-
================================
cd /usr/src
rm -fv csf.tgz
wget https://download.configserver.com/csf.tgz
tar -xzf csf.tgz
cd csf
sh install.sh


URL: https://malware.expert/howto/configure-csf-with-cpanel-server/
